# UI — conventions

## Select — always shadcn, never native `<select>`

```svelte
import * as Select from '$lib/components/ui/select'

<!-- ✅ Correct — always specify type="single" or type="multiple" -->
<Select.Root type="single" value={genre} onValueChange={(v) => (genre = v)}>
  <Select.Trigger class="h-9 text-sm">
    {genre ? labelFor(genre) : 'Placeholder'}
  </Select.Trigger>
  <Select.Content>
    <Select.Item value="opt1" label="Option 1" />
  </Select.Content>
</Select.Root>

<!-- ❌ Forbidden -->
<select bind:value={genre}>...</select>
```

For "all" / empty option use the sentinel `'__all__'`, not an empty string:

```svelte
value={genre || '__all__'}
onValueChange={(v) => (genre = v === '__all__' ? '' : v)}
```

## Buttons — hover states are required

```svelte
<!-- outline style -->
<button class="rounded-md border px-3 py-2 text-sm hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground">

<!-- primary style -->
<button class="rounded-md bg-primary px-3 py-2 text-sm text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90">

<!-- destructive -->
<button class="rounded-md border border-destructive text-destructive hover:bg-destructive/10">
```

Global `transition-all duration-150` and `active:scale-[0.97]` are applied to all buttons via `app.css`.

## Media type chips

```svelte
import { getMediaTypeMeta } from '$shared/lib/labels'

<span class="rounded-full border px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-semibold {getMediaTypeMeta(item.mediaType).color}">
  {getMediaTypeMeta(item.mediaType).label}
</span>
```

## Watch status icons

Use `style=` for colour, not a dynamic Tailwind class variable:

```svelte
import { WATCH_STATUS_META } from '$shared/config/domain'
{@const statusMeta = WATCH_STATUS_META[item.status ?? 'PLAN_TO_WATCH']}

<div class="rounded-full p-1 text-white shadow" style="background-color: {statusMeta.bgColor}">
  {#if statusMeta.icon === 'circle-check'}<CircleCheckIcon />
  {:else if statusMeta.icon === 'circle-play'}<CirclePlayIcon />
  {:else}<ClockIcon />
  {/if}
</div>
```

## Media cards (grid)

Cards are links with `group relative overflow-hidden`. Poster + absolute hover overlay at the bottom. Status icon — `absolute top-2 right-2`.

```svelte
<a href="/media/{id}" class="group relative block overflow-hidden rounded-lg border bg-card">
  <img class="aspect-2/3 w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105" .../>
  <!-- status icon -->
  <div class="absolute top-2 right-2 ...">...</div>
  <!-- hover overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black/90 ... opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100">...</div>
  <!-- static footer -->
  <div class="p-3 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-0">...</div>
</a>
```

## Countries

Always display as a full localised name with flag:

```svelte
import { formatCountry } from '$shared/lib/labels'
{formatCountry('US')}  // 🇺🇸 United States
```

## Global styles (app.css)

- `button` — `transition-all duration-150`, `cursor-pointer`, `active:scale-[0.97]`
- `a` — `transition-colors duration-150`
- `input:focus-visible` — `border-ring` + ring via `color-mix`
